Fourth Department,

February, 1983

(February 28, 1983) The People of the State of New York, Respondent, v George Starks, Appellant.

— Judgment unanimously affirmed. Appellant’s motion to strike appendix from respondent’s brief granted. (Appeal from judgment of Monroe County Court, Bergin, J. — grand larceny, third degree.) Present — Dillon, P. J., Callahan, Denman, Moule and Schnepp, JJ.
